    dc:description "FIGURE 44. Biemna rhabdotylostylota sp. nov., a, habitus of holotype RMNH Por. 9927 (scale bar = 1 cm), b, light microscopic image of the skeleton showing the diversity of mega- and microscleres, c – j, SEM images of spicules, c, large tylostyle, c 1, details of c, d, small tylostyle, e, large rhabdotylostyle, e 1, details of e, f, small rhabdotylostyle, f 1, details of f, g, large sigma, h, small sigma, i, long trichodragma, i 1, detail of i showing individual long microxeas, j, short trichodragma, j 1, detail of j showing individual short microxeas." ;
